  h2.author-bio__heading About the Author: Jason Lengstorf
  .author-bio__text
    h3.author-bio__subheading I’m living Post-Hustle.
    .author-bio__content
      p After years spent in the “Hustle &amp; Grind” culture — the always-on, anything-for-success slog in pursuit of More™ — I finally asked myself the question I should have asked a long time ago: #[strong “Why do I work?”]
      p I work to give myself a better life. Work shouldn’t be standing between me and an enjoyable life — and that’s what Post-Hustle is all about.
